{
  "title": "Xtra Silky Italian Myeongnan Roe Frittata",
  "description": "A fresh and silky Italian-inspired dish featuring myeongnan-roe, perfect for a nostalgic breakfast or brunch",
  "cuisine": "Italian",
  "diet": [
